'''Witold Hensel''' (born March 29, 1917, died on November 22, 2008 in [[Warsaw]]) was a [[Poland|Polish]] [[archaeologist]]. He was a member of the [[Polish Academy of Sciences]] and a member of the [[Sejm]] in [[People's Republic of Poland|PRL]] ([[Democratic Party (Poland)|SD]], 1985-1989).

